            <abstract>
                <p>Miracle of <persName ref="PRS4377Gabriel"/> about the building of a church dedicated to St Gabriel in the country 
                    Neqlon with mentioning of a blind person, who asked about the completion of the work while the construction began. This 
                    miracle is very similar to <ref type="work" corresp="LIT7810MiyazMir"/> and thematically similar to 
                    <ref type="work" corresp="LIT7786SaneHomily"/>. It may form part of the monthly reading for the 19th of Gǝnbot in the 
                    <ref type="work" corresp="LIT1284Dersan"/>.</p>
            </abstract>
